content: chuasonglin1995: Merged two significant PRs: #2329 adding a new 0x plugin for swapping on EVMs (+88.5k/-13.2k lines) and #2195 refactoring websearch into a service (+31k/-3.2k lines), representing substantial codebase changes across 790 files. Maintained consistent activity across 5 days, balancing refactoring work (45%) with feature development and bug fixes, while also creating issue #2192 about Docker image building and providing feedback through 9 comments on issues and PRs.
